      <title>Concord 最初的开发合同价值 2 亿美元，但索尼最终花费的成本却高得多 - 报告</title>
      <link>https://www.ign.com/articles/concords-initial-development-deal-was-200-million-but-it-wound-up-costing-sony-much-more-report</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据 Firewalk Studios 关闭后的一份报告，Concord 的初始开发协议价值约为 2 亿美元，由此可见索尼为开发这款灾难性的实时服务游戏花费了多少资金，这款游戏仅持续了两周就被无情地关闭了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.ign.com/articles/concords-initial-development-deal-was-200-million-but-it-wound-up-costing-sony-much-more-report</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 00:08:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>EA 老板称 BioWare 凭借《龙腾世纪》重拾优势，并预测《龙腾世纪》将因“竞争有限”而具有“突破潜力”</title>
      <link>https://www.ign.com/articles/ea-boss-says-bioware-has-returned-to-its-strengths-with-dragon-age-predicts-breakout-potential-thanks-in-part-to-limited-competition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[EA 首席执行官安德鲁·威尔逊 (Andrew Wilson) 表示，随着《龙腾世纪：面纱守卫》即将发布，BioWare 已重拾强劲实力，他高度赞扬了这款游戏的评价，并预测由于竞争有限，这款游戏具有“突破潜力”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.ign.com/articles/ea-boss-says-bioware-has-returned-to-its-strengths-with-dragon-age-predicts-breakout-potential-thanks-in-part-to-limited-competition</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 22:27:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
